node.text:
My prayers go out to the family of Police Officer Ella French. She was only 29 years old. 

She was shot in the head during a traffic stop last night in Chicago. 

God be with her family! We MUST STAND WITH OUR POLICE!! WE MUST END THIS HATRED TOWARD OUR MEN AND WOMEN IN BLUE!!
